Package net.smartcosmos.model.event

Core event definitions that facilitate near real-time integration with external components authorized via OAuth 2.0, whereby the events are delivered to an INotificationEndpoint.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEvent
    Flexible mechanism for capturing user interactions with the platform.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EventType
    Collection of SMART COSMOS events that capture virtually all interactions between a user and the platform.
